Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个兵器拥有打破世界的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将世界引同灭亡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像巴哈姆特一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得故乡的奶奶说过以前经常去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去妮娜的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禀报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越狱的贞德·达克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦罗·雷欧涅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜·朵兰格的行踪目前还未查到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘的小孩的情况也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.99,0:01:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已对凯撒·利德法尔德进行过拷问了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他什么都设说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是奥尔良骑士团的团长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多练练再来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越狱犯就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去艾博斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要见你 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亚思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢房生活已经步入正轨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起铁栏杆 你还是更适合握剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士团情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长都被抓了 还能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亚思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔良骑士团就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见到贞德大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔良骑士团必将复活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要让骑士团跟贞德大人一起重获荣光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给贞德大人和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能直接叫妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 妮娜回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 瞅瞅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是莫拉 叫瞅瞅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何叫瞅瞅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我朋友 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在王都流行这种衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要丟下你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我故乡的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是贞德...达克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是摆设哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你变瘦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朋友贞德说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 你去过神界的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我们怎么去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你啦 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吗 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥...自便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2000年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神与恶魔齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了巴哈姆特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时背着精疲力尽的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送他们回到了神界的正是老朽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来啦 又是这一段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我当年的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 帅气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是迷上老朽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这背 怎么坐嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论如何都要去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还望您助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 睡着就叫不醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的温泉可厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能疗伤 还能去除疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹的爸爸帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还叫那位大人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟恋爰不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 小孩不是爱的结晶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人 如今仍在守护着我和艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有倾心的男性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要接近帅气的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变成龙大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此一直无法跟倾心的人好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 唯独能跟那人一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟他在一起就很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至觉得我来到世上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了跟他跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是初恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德的初恋是怎样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在春心萌动之前就收到了启示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以神的仆人的身份上战场了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的仆人不能恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿妮娜能跟那人过上幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我也不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明人超好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然干了那么多可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此仍然喜欢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我依然无法恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中也有多个面目各异的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有两张相反的面目也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:14:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妮娜能爱上他的所有面目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份恋情也许就是真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好看得很 好看得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜要待多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要去趟神界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神界？我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不是说去就去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去神界干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见姆伽罗妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹是贞德的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是失散的神圣之子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣之子？什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,编吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家就是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣之子就是神圣之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是问你神圣之子是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝水的话 那里有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话 要聊几句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是个很神奇的村子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次来也很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不是龙族来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山脚的村子出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是嫁过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜真是个好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:16:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 寄养在我们家的孩子们的父母画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子的日子也不好过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都出去赚钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜的父亲也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的父亲已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 为了保护村子不被火球砸中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子有没有突然变龙你们添麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 她救了我们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那孩子也长大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自从父亲死的那天开始就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要靠近跟她父亲年纪相仿的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变成龙大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不去回想痛苦的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你当她的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这人根本不值得感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对妮娜的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看过她有多亲近你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你对妮娜有多好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都喊你收敛点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻耳子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候就该说那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要娶你当团长夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊 团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 副团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是奥尔良骑士团的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我不就开个玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 刻耳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩睡好没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡得可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真打算去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 要怎么去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 坐我背上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你那小身板...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带着天使回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 路上当心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好保护贞德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就突破极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 你擅长什么料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然提起这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长什么啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神击的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之都 P1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长什么啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 咋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用汤煮菜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是汤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.13,0:24:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还望下集继续关照
